WEBVTT

00:14:59.500 --> 00:15:01.601
That's not our problem.

00:15:01.625 --> 00:15:04.059
We have a relationship problem,

00:15:04.083 --> 00:15:06.434
not a misinformation problem.

00:15:06.458 --> 00:15:09.184
Misinformation is the symptom,

00:15:09.208 --> 00:15:10.726
not the cause.

00:15:10.750 --> 00:15:12.809
If people trust,

00:15:12.833 --> 00:15:17.393
they'll put up with a little risk
to avert a much bigger one.

00:15:17.417 --> 00:15:20.976
The one thing that I want and I hope for

00:15:21.000 --> 00:15:24.684
is that we as a medical
and health community

00:15:24.708 --> 00:15:28.851
have the moral courage and humility

00:15:28.875 --> 00:15:31.226
to productively engage,